{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fece843c5d","title":"关于土地改革运动的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"31440dce68","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"fece843c5d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"152ecd420e","name":"阎九如"},{"id":"7b2425eca3","name":"康清"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"},{"id":"f1f40fb962","name":"周尧"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f2041510a0","type":"title","text":"关于土地改革运动的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"},{"id":"571a35c1c2","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院康清周尧阎九如","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"},{"id":"d95d943211","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“土改中农民对地主的斗争都是人为地煽动起来的，是那些所谓工作人员强迫农民去斗争的，结果把地主活活地打死。”(农机系教师　康清)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"},{"id":"e185fad0fc","type":"paragraph","text":"2．他家乡土改时，他父亲畏罪自杀。他便大哭一顿，气恨的说：“要杀，我要报仇。”(植保系教授　周尧)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"},{"id":"f5ceeca605","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“土地改革采取和平的办法也可以达到目的，象黄世仁那样的地主不多，不必采取斗争的方式，斗争太残酷了。”“土地改革政府命令把地分了就可以了，对人不应残酷，地主是社会制度遗留下来的，不能怪他本人。”“土改中多少人斗争一个人，群众的斗争情绪是残酷的。”(财务科科长　阎九如)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"},{"id":"c6a0645d4f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d"}],"page":{"id":"29fb80d1c8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fece843c5d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}